    <p class="hero-subtitle text-xl md:text-2xl mt-4 text-yellow font-bold animate-fade-in-up delay-200 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      Eliminate Friction and Accelerate Revenue Using Our Dedicated Fractional AI Growth Team
