  </div>
  </section>
</main>

<!-- Kill Zone / Engagement Latency Section -->
<section class="kill-zone-section pt-12 pb-16 md:pt-16 md:pb-24 bg-navy">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="kill-zone-headline font-bold text-yellow text-center mb-12 italic">
      It's no longer "the big that beats the small"
      <br class="md:hidden" />
      it's "the fast that runs over the slow"
    </h2>

    <!-- Kill Zone Graphic (CSS/SVG) -->
    <div class="kill-zone-graphic mx-auto max-w-4xl mb-6">
      <div class="kill-zone-wrapper">
        <!-- Labels -->
        <div class="kill-zone-labels">
          <div class="kill-zone-label-left">
            <span class="kill-zone-end-label">Customer<br/>Interest</span>
          </div>
          <div class="kill-zone-label-right">
            <span class="kill-zone-end-label">Business<br/>Response</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The hazard bar -->
        <div class="kill-zone-bar">
          <!-- Left icon circle -->
          <div class="kill-zone-icon kill-zone-icon-left">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-navy" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M3 13h1v7c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-7h1a1 1 0 0 0 .7-1.7l-9-9a1 1 0 0 0-1.4 0l-9 9A1 1 0 0 0 3 13z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <!-- Center text -->
          <div class="kill-zone-center-text">
            <span class="kill-zone-bar-title">The Kill Zone (Engagement Latency)</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Right icon circle -->
          <div class="kill-zone-icon kill-zone-icon-right">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-navy" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20 3H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v11c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h7v2H8v2h8v-2h-3v-2h7c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 13H4V5h16v11z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <!-- Caption below bar -->
          <div class="kill-zone-sublabel">
            <span class="kill-zone-caption">Engagement Latency: The time gap between customer interest and your business's meaningful response.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Copy blocks -->
    <div class="kill-zone-copy-wrap max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <div>
        <p class="kill-zone-copy">
          Your competition is already <span class="text-yellow">closing this gap with AI.</span><br/>
          If you don't program <span class="text-yellow">instantaneous response, you're invisible.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="kill-zone-copy">
        Speed is now the ultimate currency and 'lead response latency' is the difference between closing a deal and losing it to a competitor who instantly responds.
      </p>

      <p class="kill-zone-copy">
        Most companies believe buying updated software fixes this, but they lack the adaptive ecosystem to make it work.
      </p>

      <p class="kill-zone-copy">
        You have the tools... but not the strategy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Friction Graphic -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <Image
        src={frictionGraphic}
        alt="Friction - workflow showing Login, Data Entry, Form Submission, Platform Switch, Approval Workflow, Report Generation, Client Portal, Syncing, Task Manager, Server"
        class="mx-auto max-w-4xl w-full friction-graphic"
        widths={[400, 768, 1024]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

